            <div class="item active" style="max-width:480px;">
              <h2>REQUEST MONEY AT THE REAL EXCHANGE RATE</h2>
              <p>The money arrives in your bank account within 2 business days.</p>
			  <a class="startreq">Start Requesting</a>
            </div>
