		<h3 class="steps">3 SIMPLE STEPS TO GETTING PAID</h3>
		<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-24 stepsimgs">
			<%= image_tag("createnew.png", :alt => "createnew", :class => "chiimg") %>
			<h4>1. Create a request</h4>
			<p>Enter how much, what it’s for, and your bank account for where the money goes.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-24 stepsimgs">
			<%= image_tag("sharecpu.png", :alt => "createnew", :class => "chiimg") %>
			<h4>2. Share it</h4>
			<p>Send the request link to your payer any way you'd like.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-24 stepsimgs">
			<%= image_tag("getpaid.png", :alt => "createnew", :class => "chiimg") %>
			<h4>3. Get paid</h4>
			<p>Your payer joins TradeNAIRA and pays. You'll get an email when it's all done.</p>
		</div>
        <div class="col-xs-24 text-center">
                <a class="startsave" style="margin:20px auto;">Learn More</a>
        </div>

	  	<div class="vertical-align-center hidden-xs nav-next-section col-xs-24">
	     		<i class="fa fa-angle-down gotonext" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#38a6cb;"></i>
	  	</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-24 businessdiv">
