		<div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-24">
			<h3 class="business">BUSINESSES: SAVE UP TO 8X ON INTERNATIONAL PAYMENTS</h3>
			<p class="busicon">Asking customers to pay you through TradeNAIRA? Simply send them a request to avoid messy bank details and make sure you get the right amount. They'll need to join TradeNAIRA to pay.</p>
			<p class="busicon">TradeNAIRA always converts your money at the real exchange rate and charges a fair & transparent fee - so you save big time versus the big guys.</p>
			<a class="findmore">Find out more about requesting money</a>
		</div>
